title: Vote now for #GameOnVarsity Game of the Week!
text:
Vote now for #GameOnVarsity Game of the Week! Eight teams, four matchups, one winner. Help us decide which team to spotlight this Friday night! Post to Facebook Vote now for #GameOnVarsity Game of the Week! Eight teams, four matchups, one winner. Help us decide which team to spotlight this Friday night!  //on.wusa9.com/1LogYAI   Join the Conversation To   Vote now for #GameOnVarsity Game of the Week! Grace E Olson, 5:04 p.m. EDT October 10, 2015 #GameOnVarsity Game of the Week contest 10-16-15 (Photo: WUSA9) CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
We've narrowed the field down to four games. Now, it's up to you to chose our Game of the Week winning matchup! 
The two winning teams will be treated like WUSA9 Sports royalty, as we showcase your school in our GAME ON Varsity show with interviews, highlights and more. Vote early, vote often and spread the word. 
The poll closes Thursday night at 8PM. 
Contenders: St. Albans vs. Georgetown Prep Anacostia vs. Coolidge
